== Spanish ==
=== Etymology ===
''[[coño]]'' + ''-azo'', "giant [[cunt]]"

=== Noun ===
'''coñazo''' (''vulgar'')
# (''Spain'') An extreme annoyance.
#: ''¡Qué coñazo!'' "How extremely annoying!", lit. "what a giant cunt!"
# (''Venezuela'') Hit, blow. Also, meaning "all of a sudden".
#: ''Le dieron un coñazo en la cara.'' "He was hit in the face".
#: ''Ha sido un coñazo para ella.'' "It's been a great blow to her".
#: ''Todo sucedió de coñazo.'' "Everything happened all of a sudden".

